 you know the date. You can&rsquo;t start your Adoption Leave before your child enters Great Britain.</p>\n\n<h3>Third notification stage</h3>\n<p>You must tell your employer the date your child actually entered Great Britain - within 28 days of the date of entry.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You can change your Adoption Leave start date if you give your employer at least 28 days’ notice - you can change the end date if you give 8 weeks’ notice.</p>\n</div>\n"}]},"tags":[{"title":"Holidays, time off, sick leave, maternity and paternity leave","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/working%2Ftime-off.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes career breaks and the holiday entitlement calculator","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=working%2Ftime-off","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/working/time-off"},"parent":{"title":"Working, jobs and pensions","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/working.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes holidays and finding a job","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=working","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/working"},"parent":null}},{"title":"Having a child, parenting and adoption","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/births-deaths-marriages%2Fchild-adoption.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Legal rights, birth certificates, parental rights and child maintenance","short_description":"","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=births-deaths-marriages%2Fchild-adoption","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/births-deaths-marriages/child-adoption"},"parent":{"title":"Births, deaths, marriages and care","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/births-deaths-marriages.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes civil partnerships, splitting up and Lasting Power of Attorney","short_descr